CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Maryland Horse Industry Board – Sunset Extension
3 FOR the purpose of continuing the Maryland Horse Industry Board in accordance with the
4 provisions of the Maryland Program Evaluation Act (sunset law) by extending to a
5 certain date the termination provisions relating to the statutory and regulatory
6 authority of the Board; and generally relating to the Maryland Horse Industry
7 Board.
8 BY repealing and reenacting, without amendments,
9 Article – Agriculture
10 Section 2–703
11 Annotated Code of Maryland
12 (2016 Replacement Volume and 2025 Supplement)
13 BY repealing and reenacting, with amendments,
