5 Act, the provisions of this subtitle and of any rule or regulation adopted under this subtitle
6 shall terminate and be of no effect after July 1, [2026] 2036.
7 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect June
8 1, 2026.
